text: Vadim Shikarev (15 November 1968 - February 2001) was a Kazakhstani archer. Shikarev competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics, the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Vadim ShikarevVadim KURALES == References == Category:1968 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Kazakhstani archers Category:Olympians for Kazakhstan
